&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent&lt;strong&gt; premier&lt;/strong&gt; gaming and betting operators at &lt;strong&gt;events, bars, casinos, and entertainment venues&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
